OL,3,C'The driver of that HGV has destroyed
OL,4,Cmy life': Man jailed for three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FWatch: Drone footage shows the
OL,8,Faftermath of the collision along the
OL,9,FChichester bypass.
OL,11,FA dangerous lorry driver, who crashed
OL,12,Finto other vehicles at high speed in
OL,13,FChichester, has been jailed.
OL,15,FKuljinder Singh, 45, was driving a
OL,16,FMercedes HGV when he crashed into the
OL,17,Frear of a van, travelling more than
OL,18,F50mph on the A27.
