OL,3,C'The driver of that HGV has destroyed
OL,4,Cmy life': Man jailed for three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FThe incident took place at about
OL,8,F4.15pm on August 8, 2022, on the dual
OL,9,Fcarriageway eastbound between the
OL,10,FFishbourne and Stockbridge roundabouts.
OL,12,FFootage from inside his lorry showed
OL,13,FSingh failing to notice stationary
OL,14,Ftraffic ahead of him in lane one.
OL,16,FHe was recorded still accelerating at
OL,17,Fthe moment of impact, which left three
OL,18,Fpeople with life-changing injuries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
