OL,3,C'The driver of that HGV has destroyed
OL,4,Cmy life': Man jailed for three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FSingh, of Ennis Square, Redcar, North
OL,8,FYorkshire, was arrested and charged
OL,9,Fwith three counts of causing serious
OL,10,Finjury by dangerous driving.
OL,12,FHe admitted the charges and at
OL,13,FPortsmouth Crown Court he was
OL,14,Fsentenced to three years and ten
OL,15,Fmonths in prison on 10 October.
OL,17,FSingh was also disqualified from
OL,18,Fdriving for four years and 11 months.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
