OL,4,Cmy life': Man jailed for three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FSussex Police found no evidence Singh
OL,8,Fhad been using a mobile phone while
OL,9,Fdriving, and he was not intoxicated.
OL,11,FThe collision with three other
OL,12,Fvehicles left one car overturned on
OL,13,Fits roof.
OL,15,FThe victim in the overturned car
OL,16,Fcontinues to suffer from life-changing
OL,17,Finjuries.
