OL,3,C'The driver of that HGV has destroyed
OL,4,Cmy life': Man jailed for three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FTwo men who were in the van
OL,8,Fimmediately in front of the lorry also
OL,9,Fcontinue to suffer the life-changing
OL,10,Fimpact of the crash.
OL,12,FOne of the men said: "This has changed
OL,13,Fmy life in every way, I now live with
OL,14,Fthe lasting trauma of what happened.
OL,16,F"I remember waking up in the front
OL,17,Fpassenger seat, I had previously been
OL,18,Funconscious. The reason I awoke was
OL,19,Fbecause I was choking on my own blood.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
