OL,3,C'The driver of that HGV has destroyed
OL,4,Cmy life': Man jailed for three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"I turned to my work colleague. I had
OL,8,Fno idea if he was alive or dead.
OL,10,F"I believe this collision was
OL,11,Favoidable, I cannot understand what
OL,12,Fthe driver of a HGV has crashed into
OL,13,Fus, causing multiple vehicles to be
OL,14,Fdestroyed and causing me to sustain
OL,15,Flife-changing injuries."
OL,17,FThe driver of the van added: "I am
OL,18,Ffrustrated that the driver has never
OL,19,Fexplained personally why or how the
OL,20,Fcollision occurred."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
