OL,3,C'The driver of that HGV has destroyed
OL,4,Cmy life': Man jailed for three-car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FSergeant Mark Farrow from the Roads
OL,8,FPolicing Unit said: "This was a highly
OL,9,Fdistressing collision which highlights
OL,10,Fthe devastating impact dangerous
OL,11,Fdriving has.
OL,13,F"All drivers need to be alert at the
OL,14,Fwheel, especially lorry drivers who
OL,15,Fpose a greater risk of harm to other
OL,16,Froad users.
OL,18,F"It is a miracle that no one was
OL,19,Fkilled on the road that day, and
OL,20,FSingh's driving fell far below the
OL,21,Fstandard of a competent driver.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
