OL,7,F"This case should be a warning to all
OL,8,Fdrivers about road safety. We are
OL,9,Fpleased that a dangerous driver has
OL,10,Fbeen taken off our roads and will
OL,11,Fserve a significant custodial
OL,12,Fsentence."
